STUDENT WORKFLOW

* Visits site
** Checks to see if this is first visit or not

** If first visit do the following:
*** Display choose grade item screen
*** Once items are choosen, student click submit button
*** Once submitted, screen will dislpay total points and current grade on choosen grade items.
*** Should update on visit

** If not first visit do the following:
*** Display total points and current grade on choosen grade items.
*** Should update on visit

TEACHER WORKFLOW

* Visits site
** Grabs all the student's grades
** Computes the grades for every student
